room_title: Escape room "The Manor" by Immersion in Orange County
room_address: 1095 N Main St suite b Orange, CA 92867
room_description:
A secret is being kept within Bishop Manor. Mysterious disappearances are happening for those seeking comfort and solace for their loved ones. A well-known Mystic offers to help those in need, never to be seen again. You have been invited by an unknown source to try and solve the mystery of Bishop Manner. 
You received an invitation to arrive at precisely this date and time with the promise of adventure and mystery, not knowing what to expect, you are intrigued. With a limited amount of time, do you have what it takes to escape from Bishop Manor?
